  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial will study a possible effect of standard Israeli breakfast (30% of caloric value
      and 21 gram protein) on cognitive and executive functions (working memory, visual memory,
      concentration and coordination), on patients with mild-moderate liver cirrhosis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
